{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/gif2.gif?t=1717013482\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Description:</h2>Embark on an epic quest to defend the sacred crystal from relentless waves of monstrous invaders. Harness your unique combat skills, strategically deploy your powerful turrets, and reach your full potential to push back the dark forces. Will you rise as the ultimate defender or succumb to the shadows?<br>   <br>The fate of the crystal rests in your hands. Will you rise to the occasion and stand as an unwavering sentinel against the encroaching darkness, or will the hordes succeed in shattering the last remnants of hope? Your decisions, reflexes, and strategy will determine the outcome of &quot;Eternal Vigil&quot;. Defend the crystal at all costs and etch your name into the annals of legendary defenders.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Intense Combat Variety :</strong> Engage in heart-pounding battles up close or at a distance using an array of weapons, from swift blades to powerful bows and staves.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/ezgif-4-bdfea2ccc6.gif?t=1717013482\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Turrets:</strong> Strategically position powerful turrets to defend the sacred crystal against relentless waves of diverse and challenging enemy creatures. Make sure to upgrade the turrets to match their increasing strength.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/ezgif-4-12ff8b84d6.gif?t=1717013482\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Empowering Abilities:</strong> Unleash an arsenal of awe-inspiring abilities that turn the tide of battle, ensuring you're always one step ahead of the enemy onslaught.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/intense_combat.gif?t=1717013482\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Shady Mario:</strong> At the shopkeeper you can find a large selection of magical items such as weapons, armor, and turrets as well as empowering potions to arm yourself against the incoming waves. Be cautious, after all, his is nickname is &quot;Shady&quot; Mario.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/mario_shop.gif?t=1717013482\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Unpredictable Crystal Elements:</strong> Embrace the chaos of shifting crystal energies. Each Crystal: Light, Lightning, Water, &amp; Fire\u2014bestows unique stats and abilities, tailoring your strategy with every unpredictable shift. As you harness their power, prepare for future expansions that will deepen your tactical arsenal. Dive into a game where adaptability is your greatest weapon.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2543750/extras/crystals.png?t=1717013482\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Is this all you have?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/a9fa34fd1488922fdf192cc8007c7d4bb31caf71.jpg"},{"name":"Lucky Warden","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/0c8fb03098fed84f5e1f00ebaf0f59807781877f.jpg"},{"name":"Berserker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/b3ddc7ec63d8698ceedb0be1231c6536177f1745.jpg"},{"name":"Unreachable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/5a5f33174817d638be5af7745f50dbb6395c2663.jpg"},{"name":"Tireless Patrol","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/86534dd6c7a88918bba35a0cc496aaa61c33f15f.jpg"},{"name":"Taste of Victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2543750/